{
  "3127710": {
    "name": "CONCRETE",
    "steam_appid": 3127710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127710/extras/4a5b7d370e757157561faa04c5d979a0.avif?t=1754578941\" width=600 height=184 /></span><i>Strange statues have begun to materialise across the abandoned world of CONCRETE. They hold an unnatural grip on the minds of the recently missing population.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hired to explore this desolate world, you must rely on your wits, surroundings, and navigational skills to find and destroy these ominous figures.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIRST PERSON EXPLORATION</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move freely through environments with a weighty and responsive player character</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ATMOSPHERIC IMMERSION </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover an atmospheric, isolated, and abandoned world presented with a retro flare</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PHYSICAL OBJECTS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with and manipulate objects scattered around the environment, such as crates, barrels, soda cans, books, and many, <strong>MANY</strong> more</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use these to your advantage, like stacking a pile of crates to climb over a high wall</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NOTES AND SECRETS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Read notes to piece together information and secrets from environmental clues </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2-4 HOUR LONG EXPERIENCE</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 large unique maps to explore packed with statues to find, puzzles to solve, secrets to discover, challenges to overcome, and an ever-present dark and foreboding atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition: 4 collectable minigames, 30 hidden VHS tapes, 48 achievements, and plenty of fun to be had stacking crates as high as you can manage</p></li></ul>",
